text: Nice condo with great location. Nice pool, only recently under painting construction so quite limited to use pool and stuff around. But once will be done then Nice painted again üôåüèªNice tennis court as well.

Too much construction going on here, so don't expect too much. Temporary bus shelter, very quick fixes, and very blind corners. So you'd better be a little more alert when you're waiting for your bus here!

Had an unpleasant experience when trying to send something to a resident here this evening. The security guard did now allow me to come in from the main entrance. I could not locate the other entrance and ended up entering together with a resident from a side gate.
